"title": "8812: riches, ungodly use of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8812",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Ungodly people often make the possession of wealth a priority. They do not understand the true nature of wealth, and they do not realise that they will have to face God in judgment.</p>\n<h2>The ungodly grow rich</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:12\">PSA 73:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:21\">LUK 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6-Jas2:7\">JAS 2:6–2:7</a></p>\n<h2>The ungodly misuse riches</h2>\n<h3>They often obtain their riches unjustly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:2\">PRO 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:5\">1KI 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">PRO 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:6\">PRO 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1-Mic2:5\">MIC 2:1–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:10-Mic6:12\">MIC 6:10–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:6-Hab2:11\">HAB 2:6–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>They accumulate and hoard their riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:26\">PRO 11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:16-Job27:17\">JOB 27:16–27:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:27\">PRO 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10-Eccl5:14\">ECC 5:10–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:3\">JAS 5:1–5:3</a></p>\n<h3>They trust in their riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5-Ps49:6\">PSA 49:5–49:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24\">JOB 31:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:7\">PSA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:7\">JER 48:7</a></p>\n<h2>The ungodly suffer difficulties because of their riches</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">PRO 15:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:7-Prov13:8\">PRO 13:7–13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16-Prov15:17\">PRO 15:16–15:17</a></p>\n<h2>The ungodly, like all people, must leave their riches to others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:10\">PSA 49:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:6\">PSA 39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:18-Eccl2:21\">ECC 2:18–2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20\">LUK 12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ warned the rich of their danger</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:24\">LUK 6:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:25\">LUK 16:25</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the ungodly rich</h2>\n<h3>Nabal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:2-1Sam25:3\">1SA 25:2–25:3</a></p>\n<h3>Rich young ruler</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:23\">MRK 10:17–10:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:24\">MAT 19:16–19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:25\">LUK 18:18–18:25</a></p>",
